data.description: Beautiful townhome built in 2022 boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 1 car garage.  Enjoy natural lighting from the large stairwell windows. Nicely updated with quartz counter tops, wood cabinets and lots of extras. Beautiful patio landscaping with oversized patio. Desirable location just minutes from the beautiful Florida Keys, Turnpike, Florida Keys Outlet Mall, Baptist Hospital, restaurants, and more. Lots of great things coming to Homestead!  Use preferred lender and receive $2,000 towards closing costs and free appraisal.
